de.osci.osci12.messagetypes

Interface ContentPackageI

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AcceptDelivery, ForwardDelivery, MediateDelivery, PartialStoreDelivery, ProcessDelivery, ResponseToFetchAbstract, ResponseToFetchDelivery, ResponseToMediateDelivery, ResponseToPartialFetchDelivery, ResponseToProcessDelivery, StoreDelivery, StoredMessage

    public interface ContentPackageI
    Dieses Interface wird von allen Nachrichtentypen implementiert, die Inhaltsdaten enthalten.
